label: maximumStandardValueSpecifiedObservationResultCharacteristic
comment: A maximum standard value of the values for the characteristic observed or measured by using the specified type of observation for this sample observation result.

rangeIncludes.comment: Specifies the type of the performed observation and the acquired values of this observation on the sample.

domainIncludes.comment: A collection of diagnostic data, visual or technical, and processing data, performed on a sample.
